[{\"begin\": 3193, \"end\": 3199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7711481973455582e-11, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 3260, \"end\": 3266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.688474668830119, \"rank\": 0.45205555936777003, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 3267, \"end\": 3277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"score\": 0.9999994704754992, \"rank\": 4.721487649801767e-07, \"text\": \"Polynesian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\"}, {\"begin\": 3298, \"end\": 3311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michel_Bourez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michel Bourez\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michel_Bourez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michel_Bourez\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sight locals\", \"from\": 3162, \"to\": 3176}, {\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Back in the day, there were no kids surfing,\\\" said Bourez, who first hopped on a board as a teenager.\", \"from\": 3319, \"to\": 3421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 3328, \"to\": 3335}, {\"ngram\": \"no kids\", \"from\": 3348, \"to\": 3355}, {\"ngram\": \"Bourez\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3377}, {\"ngram\": \"a board\", \"from\": 3399, \"to\": 3406}, {\"ngram\": \"a teenager\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Teahupo'o has been a coveted destination for surfers from around the world for decades, it's only in more recent years that local surf culture and talent among younger generations began to develop across Tahiti.\", \"from\": 3423, \"to\": 3640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3633, \"end\": 3639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7711481973455582e-11, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a coveted destination\", \"from\": 3448, \"to\": 3469}, {\"ngram\": \"surfers\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3481}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3503}, {\"ngram\": \"decades\", \"from\": 3508, \"to\": 3515}, {\"ngram\": \"more recent years\", \"from\": 3530, \"to\": 3547}, {\"ngram\": \"local surf culture\", \"from\": 3553, \"to\": 3571}, {\"ngram\": \"talent\", \"from\": 3576, \"to\": 3582}, {\"ngram\": \"younger generations\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With two French Polynesian surfers included in the 2024 Olympics, the surfing community expects local interest in the sport to grow.\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3773, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3650, \"end\": 3656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.688474668830119, \"rank\": 0.45205555936777003, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 3657, \"end\": 3667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"score\": 0.9999994704754992, \"rank\": 4.721487649801767e-07, \"text\": \"Polynesian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 3688, \"to\": 3705}, {\"ngram\": \"the surfing community\", \"from\": 3707, \"to\": 3728}, {\"ngram\": \"local interest\", \"from\": 3737, \"to\": 3751}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3755, \"to\": 3764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Locals said Bourez has been a steward in the development of local surfing talent and culture in recent years.\", \"from\": 3775, \"to\": 3884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Locals\", \"from\": 3775, \"to\": 3781}, {\"ngram\": \"Bourez\", \"from\": 3787, \"to\": 3793}, {\"ngram\": \"a steward\", \"from\": 3803, \"to\": 3812}, {\"ngram\": \"the development\", \"from\": 3816, \"to\": 3831}, {\"ngram\": \"local surfing talent\", \"from\": 3835, \"to\": 3855}, {\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 3860, \"to\": 3867}, {\"ngram\": \"recent years\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 3883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Partly driven by the lack of resources he had when starting out and then finding success in his own career, Bourez said he began training talented young local surfers he spotted across the island's shores.\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 4090, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lack\", \"from\": 3902, \"to\": 3910}, {\"ngram\": \"resources\", \"from\": 3914, \"to\": 3923}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 3973}, {\"ngram\": \"his own career\", \"from\": 3977, \"to\": 3991}, {\"ngram\": \"Bourez\", \"from\": 3993, \"to\": 3999}, {\"ngram\": \"talented young local surfers\", \"from\": 4023, \"to\": 4051}, {\"ngram\": \"the island's shores\", \"from\": 4070, \"to\": 4089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Otherwise, all the knowledge that I gained during all these years will be gone - and for no reason,\\\" Bourez said.\", \"from\": 4092, \"to\": 4206, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the knowledge\", \"from\": 4104, \"to\": 4121}, {\"ngram\": \"all these years\", \"from\": 4143, \"to\": 4158}, {\"ngram\": \"no reason\", \"from\": 4182, \"to\": 4191}, {\"ngram\": \"Bourez\", \"from\": 4194, \"to\": 4200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have to give back to the local community and surfers.\\\"\", \"from\": 4207, \"to\": 4265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the local community\", \"from\": 4232, \"to\": 4251}, {\"ngram\": \"surfers\", \"from\": 4256, \"to\": 4263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Goold is one of the young local surfers Bourez has mentored.\", \"from\": 4267, \"to\": 4327, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Goold\", \"from\": 4267, \"to\": 4272}, {\"ngram\": \"the young local surfers\", \"from\": 4283, \"to\": 4306}, {\"ngram\": \"Bourez\", \"from\": 4307, \"to\": 4313}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Growing up in French Polynesia, Goold said she has spent time on the ocean since before she could remember, but only got serious about surfing around age 8.\", \"from\": 4328, \"to\": 4484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"French Polynesia\", \"from\": 4342, \"to\": 4358}, {\"ngram\": \"Goold\", \"from\": 4360, \"to\": 4365}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4385, \"to\": 4389}, {\"ngram\": \"the ocean\", \"from\": 4393, \"to\": 4402}, {\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 4478, \"to\": 4481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I challenge myself by doing things that maybe I do not want to do,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 4486, \"to\": 4564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 4515, \"to\": 4521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That means hitting the gym and surfing when the waves are really big.\", \"from\": 4565, \"to\": 4634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 4584, \"to\": 4591}, {\"ngram\": \"the waves\", \"from\": 4609, \"to\": 4618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just try to train really hard.\\\"\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4669, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Goold said she feels it's paid off: she's traveled internationally to compete and won youth tournaments at home in French Polynesia.\", \"from\": 4671, \"to\": 4803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4793, \"end\": 4802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9984275903892936, \"rank\": 0.0015748859766186259, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Goold\", \"from\": 4671, \"to\": 4676}, {\"ngram\": \"youth tournaments\", \"from\": 4757, \"to\": 4774}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 4778, \"to\": 4782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But most days, she can be found with other young surfers along the shores of Tahiti, catching waves and playfully competing against each other.\", \"from\": 4805, \"to\": 4948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4882, \"end\": 4888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7711481973455582e-11, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other young surfers\", \"from\": 4842, \"to\": 4861}, {\"ngram\": \"the shores\", \"from\": 4868, \"to\": 4878}, {\"ngram\": \"waves\", \"from\": 4899, \"to\": 4904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We keep pushing each other,\\\" Goold said with a laugh.\", \"from\": 4950, \"to\": 5004, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Goold\", \"from\": 4980, \"to\": 4985}, {\"ngram\": \"a laugh\", \"from\": 4996, \"to\": 5003}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We just hang out, and it's super fun.\\\"\", \"from\": 5005, \"to\": 5044, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"super fun\", \"from\": 5033, \"to\": 5042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The inclusion of two French Polynesian surfers - Vahin\\u00e9 Fierro and Kauli Vaast - in the Paris Olympics also has been a major boost for the promotion and development of local surfing, Bourez said.\", \"from\": 5046, \"to\": 5241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5067, \"end\": 5073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.688474668830119, \"rank\": 0.45205555936777003, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"]