\": \"young local surfers\", \"from\": 5331, \"to\": 5350}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is the best thing in the world, because I was them a couple years ago,\\\" Vaast said after winning his second round heat.\", \"from\": 5353, \"to\": 5478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5431, \"end\": 5436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best thing\", \"from\": 5362, \"to\": 5376}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5380, \"to\": 5389}, {\"ngram\": \"his second round heat\", \"from\": 5456, \"to\": 5477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We try to do our best, to give the best energy, the best personality for them.\", \"from\": 5479, \"to\": 5558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best energy\", \"from\": 5511, \"to\": 5526}, {\"ngram\": \"the best personality\", \"from\": 5528, \"to\": 5548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We try to be the best example possible.\\\"\", \"from\": 5559, \"to\": 5599, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best example\", \"from\": 5572, \"to\": 5588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vahine, who was the first Tahitian wild card to claim a victory during the World Surf League at Teahupo'o, said the shift in surfing culture for French Polynesian women has been especially noticeable.\", \"from\": 5601, \"to\": 5801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5627, \"end\": 5635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999997189661, \"rank\": 2.2100608565706498e-10, \"text\": \"Tahitian\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 5676, \"end\": 5693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.238276504840372e-24, \"t